description: Lebanese food, prepared for you, with all organic ingredients and just a touch of love...Available on the go, at your work, and catering for your parties.Serving real food is important to us. Our falafel, salads, and shawarmas are made from scratch every day at our commissary. We use an abundance of organic ingredients, and make sure that our produce and meats are delivered from as short a distance as possible, allowing us to support North Carolina farmers, provide fantastic ingredients, and contribute to your health…all in one delicious wrap.
name: Gypsy Queen Cuisine
